content.rendered:
• Feminized Seeds

The exact genetics of Roadkill Skunk can vary, as different breeders may have their own versions of the strain. However, it is generally considered to be a descendant or variation of the original Skunk #1, which is a hybrid strain that has played a significant role in the development of modern cannabis genetics.

content.rendered:
The lineage of the AK47 cannabis strain is a bit of a secret, but here’s what we know! This popular hybrid was first created in 1992 by the Dutch seed bank Serious Seeds. It’s a cross between Colombian, Mexican, Thai, and Afghani strains, making it a sativa-dominant mix.

Interestingly, there are several theories behind the name “AK47.” Some say it’s a nod to the breeder and the 47 days from planting to harvest. Others think it’s named after the famous AK-47 assault rifle, although the seed bank claims it has nothing to do with that. Regardless of its name, one thing’s for sure – AK47 is a strong and beloved strain, and its genetics have even been studied scientifically!

By Kaya Seed Company

Zambian Copper x African Blueberry

Zambian Copper is a Sativa strain that is grown widely across the plateau regions of the copper belt this is a sub-strain similar to Malawi Gold.

African Blueberry is indica dominant and is a unique and highly sought-after strain of cannabis.  This strain is a hybrid of the popular Blueberry strain and an African landrace strain, resulting in a well loved combination.

content.rendered:
Road Kill Skunk x Syrian

Roadkill Skunk is a classic sativa-dominant hybrid strain originating from Florida and California in the 1970s.

Syrian Landrace cannabis refers to a traditional variety of cannabis that is indigenous to the region of Syria. These landrace strains are unique to the area and have adapted to the local environment over many generations, resulting in distinct characteristics and effects.  Cannabis has a long history in the Middle East, with evidence of its use dating back thousands of years. In Syria, cannabis has been used for both medicinal and recreational purposes. The plant is known for its ability to grow in diverse climates and can be found in various regions of the country, including the coastal areas, mountains, and the Syrian Desert

content.rendered:
Pursat – a super rare accession made in Veal Veng valley deep in the Cardamom Mountains of coastal South-Western Cambodia in Pursat Province.

Set in a beautiful valley in the rugged central Cardamom mountains, Veal Veng was once a sparsely inhabited, heavily forested area peopled by Pearic ethnic groups.

Today the valley is a mosaic of rice and orchards, many carved illegally from a forest which was pristine very recently.

A classic Cardamom mountains sativa.

content.rendered:
African Blueberry is indica dominant and is a unique and highly sought-after strain of cannabis.  This strain is a hybrid of the popular Blueberry strain and an African landrace strain, resulting in a well loved combination.

#AfricanBlueberryHybrid #IndicaLandraceSeeds #AfricanBerrySeed #BlueberryCannabisStrain #CannabisBlueberryHybrid #AfricanLandraceStrain #AfricaBlueberrySeeds

African Blueberry
